<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870901-0061 </DOCNO><HL> Bally Mfg. Redemption</HL><DD> 09/01/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> BLYBUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK) </IN><DATELINE> CHICAGO  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Bally Manufacturing Corp. said that on Sept. 15 it will redeem all shares of its Series C cumulative preferred stock at $100.50 a share. The operator of casinos, health clubs and hotels said it issued $40 million of the stock to Golden Nugget Inc. in connection with its acquisition of the Golden Nugget Casino Hotel in Atlantic City, N.J., March 1. </TEXT></DOC>